{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_05_01_short",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 じろじろ見ないで (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "今回オファーを受けたフェスって\n毎年夏に開催されているアイドルイベントですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this festival we received an offer for…\nIt's an idol event held every summer‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。ライブと一緒にアイドルが参加する企画も\n開催される。夏の人気イベントだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Along with the live performances‚ there will be special projects involving the idols.\nIt's a popular summer event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そのフェスにサニピと月ストが\n出演することになったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest\nare going to perform at that festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7636529286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな揃って野外ステージでライブですか……\n賑やかになりそうで楽しみです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All of us will be on an outdoor stage‚ performing live…\nIt's going to be lively and exciting. I'm looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "楽しみなのはライブだけじゃないぞ\nイベントにあわせて新衣装を作ることが決まったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The excitement isn't just about the live performance.\nWe've also decided to create new outfits for the event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば千紗が新しい衣装のデザインを\n手伝うって言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Chisa said she would help\nwith the design of the new outfits.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "夏のフェスにあわせた新衣装……\nやっぱり夏っぽいイメージになるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "New outfits to match the summer festival…\nI wonder if they will have a summer-like image.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "もしデザインで要望があれば遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have any requests regarding the design‚ don't hesitate to let us know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……しいて言うなら動きやすさでしょうか\n他に要望は特にありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… if I had to say‚ it would be about ease of movement.\nOther than that‚ I don't have any specific requests.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}